young child, approximately 6 to 9 years old, small round face and wide innocent eyes
child, approximately 10 to 12 years old, developing features and slight youthful build
pre-teen, approximately 12 to 13 years old, transitioning facial features between childhood and adolescence
teenager, approximately 14 to 17 years old, youthful angular features and lanky proportions
young adult, approximately 18 to 24 years old, fresh and fully defined features
mid-twenties to late twenties, approximately 25 to 29 years old, mature youthful features
in their thirties, approximately 30 to 39 years old, fully developed mature features
in their forties, approximately 40 to 49 years old, subtle expression lines forming around eyes and mouth
in their fifties, approximately 50 to 59 years old, visible expression lines and crow's feet
in their sixties, approximately 60 to 69 years old, defined wrinkles, weathered and distinguished appearance
in their seventies, approximately 70 to 79 years old, deep wrinkles, thinning features, aged look
elderly, approximately 80 years old or older, heavily lined face, sunken cheeks, pronounced aging
